  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nThe Divider label component is not exactly matching the figma designs:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=1338-34483&mode=design&t=WUW4HhAM8V5vswIT-4\r\n\r\nWe need to make sure this component is being rendered as expected and split the code into a style and view namespaces.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Implementation\r\n\r\nKeep in mind that this component has a `:border-top-width 1`, and the border is outside the padding, so adding this property will affect the total height of the component. by 1 unit.\r\n\r\n## Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nThe component is rendered as expected and the code has been refactored.\r\n",
